    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The state that is here is the state we \"Expose\". When doing queries to algolia we then do page - 1 because algolia is 0 based.\r\n\r\nBut inside the state, state.page = 1 means we will query page 0 on Algolia.\r\n\r\nCould you walk us through your usecase/struggle with this maybe? How did you encounter a bug, how can we reproduce it? Thanks",
